## Project Queries

### All Projects with Status

```dataview
TABLE
  status as "Status",
  priority as "Priority",
  tech-stack as "Stack"
FROM "Projects"
WHERE type = "project"
SORT priority ASC
```

### Active Projects Only

```dataview
TABLE
  status as "Status",
  live-url as "URL"
FROM "Projects"
WHERE type = "project" AND status = "active"
SORT file.mtime DESC
```

### Projects by Priority

```dataview
TABLE WITHOUT ID
  file.link as "Project",
  status as "Status"
FROM "Projects"
WHERE type = "project"
GROUP BY priority
```

### Recently Updated Projects

```dataview
TABLE
  status as "Status",
  dateformat(file.mtime, "yyyy-MM-dd") as "Modified"
FROM "Projects"
WHERE type = "project"
SORT file.mtime DESC
LIMIT 5
```

