## Journal Queries

### Recent Journal Entries

```dataview
LIST
FROM "Journal"
WHERE file.day
SORT file.day DESC
LIMIT 10
```

### Journal Entries This Month

```dataview
TABLE WITHOUT ID
  file.link as "Day",
  file.size as "Size"
FROM "Journal"
WHERE file.day.month = date(today).month AND file.day.year = date(today).year
SORT file.day DESC
```

### Journal with Specific Tag

```dataview
LIST
FROM "Journal"
WHERE contains(file.tags, "#reflection")
SORT file.day DESC
```

