## Query Patterns

### Filtering Patterns

```
// Contains text
WHERE contains(field, "value")

// Starts with
WHERE startswith(field, "prefix")

// Multiple conditions
WHERE condition1 AND condition2
WHERE condition1 OR condition2

// Negation
WHERE !completed
WHERE field != "value"

// Date comparisons
WHERE date >= date(today)
WHERE date < date(today) - dur(7 days)

// Array contains
WHERE contains(tags, "#important")
WHERE contains(file.tags, "project")
```

### Formatting Patterns

```
// Date formatting
dateformat(date, "yyyy-MM-dd")
dateformat(date, "MMMM dd, yyyy")

// Number formatting
round(number, 2)

// String operations
upper(text)
lower(text)
length(text)

// Null handling
default(field, "N/A")
```

